subject: Stadiums and Arenas
Football
Interscholastic Athletics
Accidents and Safety
lead_paragraph: Seven people sustained minor injuries when an electric cart raced unmanned from an end zone to midfield and hit several people after a high school playoff game at Cowboys Stadium on Saturday night.
